name: Wearable Code
tagline: Arduino sketch for Morse code blinking wearable
body:
### About

Wearable Code is a project based on an [Adafruit Gemma](https://www.adafruit.com/product/1222) board, a single [Neo Pixel](https://www.adafruit.com/products/1260), and a tact switch. Full instructions can be found on Instructables at [http://www.instructables.com/id/Wearable-Code/](http://www.instructables.com/id/Wearable-Code/)
